CREATE TABLE dbo.titanic_transformed_scala (
    Survived BIT,
    Pclass SMALLINT,
    Name NVARCHAR(200),
    Sex NVARCHAR(20),
    Age FLOAT,
    [Siblings_or_Spouses Aboard] SMALLINT,
    [Parents_or_Children Aboard] SMALLINT,
    Fare FLOAT,
    highFare BIT
)
WITH
(
    DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN,
    HEAP
);
